Class ClientPlanets

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am33.client.model.card.ClientCard
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am33.client.model.card.ClientPlanets
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ClientPlanets extends ClientCard
Client-side representation of a Planets adventure card. Contains all information needed for the UI to display and interact with the card, without requiring server-side logic.
